<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns ist gesagt
                            <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> wie daz grosze gewerbe in den landen an
                        vil enden seyn, und <expan>künne<ex>n</ex></expan> doch nicht gewiszen, wo
                        hin <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> auf wen sie cze cziehen mainen. Und
                                <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>, ob ir <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>söliche<ex>n</ex></expan> sachen iht west
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> het, daz ir uns das
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet bey
                                <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Erfüren wir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> iht,
                        das <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ew bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>auch</add>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>i<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan>
<expan>Laur<ex>encii.</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
